<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Support Ticket Reply</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333845;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 20, 34, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9e9eb;
    }

    .header img {
      max-height: 40px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .logo-fallback {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0e1422;
      border: 2px solid #202533;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 32px 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #5c5f6a;
    }

    .message-box {
      border-left: 3px solid #202533;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #333845;
    }

    .reply-box {
      border-left: 3px solid #4078ff;
      background-color: #f0f1ff;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #0e1422;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #878a92;
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dqcdxspmu/image/upload/v1761176863/logo_jjfkxp.png" alt="Ecommerce Logo"
        onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline-block';" />
      <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">Ecommerce</span>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= fullName %>,</p>
      <p>We’ve reviewed your support request regarding:</p>
      <p><strong>
          <%= subject %>
        </strong></p>

      <div class="message-box">
        <strong>Your message:</strong>
        <p>
          <%= userMessage %>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reply-box">
        <strong>Our reply:</strong>
        <p>
          <%= adminReply %>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>If you need further assistance, you can simply reply to this email and our support team will get back to you.
      </p>
      <p>Alternatively, you can send a new message through the contact form on our website.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px;">Best regards,<br /><strong>The Ecommerce Support Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© 2025 Ecommerce. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>